      "language": "zh",
      "created_at": "2025-07-10T14:44:29.767815",
      "source_model": "text-embedding-ada-002",
      "tags": "[\"家庭\", \"情緒\", \"健康\"]"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "f5c0138b-4d8b-471e-97b0-a61554a84081",
      "chunk_index": 11,
      "episode_id": "6867815154dac0f7fe97587a",
      "podcast_id": "1304",
      "podcast_name": "",
      "author": "",
      "category": "",
      "episode_title": "你愛他卻不敢靠近他嗎一天聽一點1697",
      "duration": "",
      "published_date": "",
      "apple_rating": 0,
      "chunk_text": "那麼長大進入關係後你就不知道怎麼樣在發生衝突依附連結斷掉的時候靠近對方把連結重新接上因為在你的生命經驗裡沒有看過好的情感修復的樣板而學校又沒有教自然你就很難長出這樣的能力再來第二個是爸媽對待你的方式",
      "embedding": [],
      "language": "zh",
      "created_at": "2025-07-10T14:44:29.770160",
      "source_model": "text-embedding-ada-002",
      "tags": "[\"教育\", \"家庭\", \"情感\"]"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "f3f673b2-def0-48cc-b7ee-de0d5cbeb857",
      "chunk_index": 12,
      "episode_id": "6867815154dac0f7fe97587a",
      "podcast_id": "1304",
